How do I calculate my rate of return (as compared to annual percentage yield)?

&#x200B;

Investment: 250,000.

&#x200B;

Term 45 weeks.

&#x200B;

Payback starting week one, 45 weekly payments of 6,111.11

&#x200B;

45 x 6,111.11 = 275,000

Thank You

